&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Square is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Business Development Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to drive the sourcing and recruitment of independent sales consultants across the UK. As Square continues its rapid expansion in the UK market, this role is critical to building and scaling our field sales force through quality recruitment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a high-impact, fast-paced role for a recruitment professional who thrives in volume hiring environments and understands the unique dynamics of recruiting self-employed sales professionals. You will be responsible for identifying, attracting, and recruiting &lt;strong&gt;20-30 independent consultants per month&lt;/strong&gt; through diverse sourcing channels. You&#39;ll work in close collaboration with Regional Sales Managers, and the Sales Enablement team to ensure a seamless candidate experience and successful integration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sourcing &amp;amp; Recruitment&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Source and attract experienced independent sales consultants&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the end-to-end recruitment process, aiming for 20 successful independent consultants per month, while prioritizing quality and speed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute creative sourcing strategies to build a strong pipeline of qualified candidates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Screen candidates for sales aptitude, entrepreneurial mindset, cultural fit, and alignment with Square&#39;s values.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct initial interviews and assessments to evaluate candidate suitability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stakeholder Management &amp;amp; Onboarding Alignment&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Regional Sales Managers and Team Leaders to understand regional hiring needs and candidate profiles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Align recruitment efforts with regional growth plans and business priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the Sales Enablement team to ensure smooth handover and onboarding of new consultants.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide regular updates on recruitment pipeline, progress against targets, and critical market insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process Optimization &amp;amp; Performance Reporting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and report on key recruitment metrics including pipeline volume, conversion rates, time-to-hire, and source effectiveness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate and up-to-date candidate data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously optimize recruitment processes

