&lt;p&gt;Zone B: $74,152.00&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Zone C: $70,018.00&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Zone D: $63,700.00&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Amounts listed above include target variable compensation.&lt;/p&gt;
